# Architecture

## Basic Architecture

## Target Architecture
This section describes the target software architecture described according [C4 Model](https://c4model.com).


### System Context
```mermaid
    C4Context
        Person_Ext(cust, "Customer", "Customer of ShopWise Webshop")
    Enterprise_Boundary(b0, "E-Commerce System") {  
        System(portal, "Webportal", "interface to ShopWise Webshop")
        System(AI, "AI Service", "AI for Query interpretation<br>and transformation")
        System(ren,"Result Render Service")  
        SystemDb(DB, "E-Commerce Database", "Holds product catalog and all orders")
        
    }
    UpdateElementStyle(AI, $offsetX="-100", $offsetY="-50")

    Rel(cust,portal,"Inputs Question in Natural language", "HTTPS PUT")
        UpdateRelStyle(cust, portal, $offsetX="-100", $offsetY="-50")

    Rel(ren,portal, "Updates Page")
        UpdateRelStyle(AI, ren, $offsetX="-40", $offsetY="0")

    Rel(AI,portal,"Transforms Question<br>to NoSQL", "RAG")
        UpdateRelStyle(AI, portal, $offsetX="-50", $offsetY="-30")

    Rel(AI,DB,"Executes Query","NoSQL")
        UpdateRelStyle(AI, DB, $offsetX="-40", $offsetY="-40")

    Rel(AI,ren,"Sends Results")
        UpdateRelStyle(AI, ren, $offsetX="-40", $offsetY="0")

    UpdateLayoutConfig($c4ShapeInRow="2", $c4BoundaryInRow="1")
```
```mermaid
    C4Context
    Boundary(b20, "Key", "Legend") {
        Person_Ext(perExt,,)
        System(app, "Application")
        SystemDb(db, "NoSQL Database")
    }

    UpdateLayoutConfig($c4ShapeInRow="20", $c4BoundaryInRow="1")
```
